<div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
  
  <div class="space-y-4">
    <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">What are the gym operating hours?</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700">Both 4 Kilo and 6 Kilo facilities are open Monday through Saturday, from 6:00 AM to 9:00 PM.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">How do I become a member?</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700">You can register through our online registration system. Click on "Become a Member" and follow the instructions. Students need to provide their valid student ID.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">What payment methods are accepted?</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700">We accept payments through bank transfer to our designated accounts at Commercial Bank of Ethiopia, Dashen Bank, and Awash Bank.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Are personal trainers available?</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700">Yes, we have certified personal trainers available at both locations. You can request a trainer through your member dashboard.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">What should I bring to the gym?</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700">Bring your member ID card, comfortable workout clothes, sports shoes, and a towel. We provide lockers for storing your belongings.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Can I freeze my membership?</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700">Yes, you can freeze your membership for up to 2 months per year. Contact the administration office to process your request.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>